Inflicts regular damage. If the user takes damage this turn before hitting, this move will fail.
This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
Raises the user's Attack and Defense by one stage each.

div.div: Krycenypse hides in rocky canyons. It stares patiently before ambushing foes with lightning-quick moves. Its chibi cuteness wins battles!
